		{"id":"legend","type":"text","text":"# 🗺️ Event Storming — Propagate DCP Change\n\nUse cases **D (Configure)** and **E (Propagate)**. Covers the full lifecycle from an admin changing a DCP setting through the `ChangeRequestLifecycle` state machine to every affected user getting updated and the Redis cache being flushed.\n\n**Colour key** — 🟧 Event · 🟦 Command · 🟩 Actor · 🟥 Policy · 🟪 Service · ⬛ Data store","x":-800,"y":-1080,"width":1600,"height":180,"color":"6"},
